                       :description => "The people behind this London-based startup used to run their own tour company in Rome, when they noticed a growing in trend in people looking for tailor-made itineraries. Tour buses and the same old, tired walk around the Colosseum just didn’t cut it anymore: Touriocity is all about making citytrips a unique, personal experience.",
