                     },
                     {
                       :title => "Radmule Labs",
                       :description => "RadMule Labs is a mobile game studio focusing on new and innovative ways of gaming. By building a game that has a token economy using OST Radmule wants to let players earn tokens they can spend on other apps in the OST network.",
